General.Name: KABE Group AB (publ.)
General.Description: KABE Group AB (publ.) manufactures and sells caravans and motorhomes. The company sells its products through retailers and dealers in Europe and the Nordic region. The company was formerly known as KABE AB (publ.) and changed its name to KABE Group AB (publ.) in July 2018. KABE Group AB (publ.) was founded in 1957 and is based in Tenhult, Sweden.
